programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Murdered For a Fake Treasure - Troadec Case
programme.desc: On March 28th 2013, the burnt body of Anne Barbot, 38 years old, is discovered in a forest of Maine-et-Loire.
programme.sub-title: Murdered For a Fake Treasure - Troadec Case

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Émilie Godest Case
programme.desc: On November 9th 2007, around 11:30PM, aid arrives on the scene of an accident at the exit of Chateney-en-France.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Savage Murder of a Mother and her Daughter (Amato Case)
programme.desc: On March 31, 2003, firefighters were called to a fire in a housing estate of Meyrargues, near Aix-en-Provence. On site, they discovered a horrific scene: the tortured and charred bodies of a mother and her daughter, Chantal and Audrey D'Amato.
programme.sub-title: The Savage Murder of a Mother and her Daughter (Amato Case)

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Life Is a Carnival, Part 1
programme.desc: Yuma gets taken for a wild ride when Kari's friend steals an extremely lucky card from the local museum. Relying on pure skill, Yuma must figure out a way to beat the luckiest guy in the world.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Life Is a Carnival, Part 2
programme.desc: Yuma’s duel atop an out-of-control monorail takes a turn for the worse when his opponent plays a Number Card that guarantees a win every time.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Foolish Fans
programme.desc: It's a dream come true for Caswell and Bronk when their favorite duelist in the world challenges them to a duel!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Shark Bait
programme.desc: Shark looks to sink his teeth into a duel with Quattro, but instead gets hooked into an underwater battle with Quattro’s sinister sibling.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Bad Developments, Part 1
programme.desc: Yuma hunts down a photographer whose pictures can predict the future. Unfortunately for Yuma and his friend Tori, it’s a future that’s not so bright.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Bad Developments, Part 2
programme.desc: Tori’s future is up in the air when the damaged airship she is on takes a turn for the worse - just as Yuma’s opponent Cameron predicted! Can Yuma save his best friend by winning his duel, or are the future photos Cameron snapped set in stone?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Double Jeopardy, Part 1
programme.desc: After accidentally falling asleep, Flip wakes up to a nightmare realization – he just slept through the first day of the World Duel Carnival.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Double Jeopardy, Part 2
programme.desc: With Astral missing, Yuma must rely on his skills alone if he wants to defeat Nistro and Dextra and save his deck and spot in the World Duel Carnival.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Pets Peeved
programme.desc: When Yuma's Heart Pieces are swiped by a pack of stray dogs, Cathy calls on her feline friends to help hunt them down. After finding the hounds' hideout, Cathy is challenged by the pack leader to a duel.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: About Hart
programme.desc: After using his powers to escape from Heartland City, Hart unleashes a path of destruction that only Yuma can help stop!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Losing Hart
programme.desc: As Kite desperately searches for his brother, Vetrix puts his diabolical plan for revenge in motion.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: A Dubious Duo
programme.desc: Vetrix continues his quest to drain Hart of all his powers.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: The Dragon Awakens
programme.desc: Kite must learn to work with Yuma if he wants to take down Trey and Quattro and rescue Hart. Can Kite put his pride aside and accept Yuma’s help, or will Kite’s ego end up sacrificing Hart’s safety?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Rock and a Hard Place
programme.desc: Faced with tough decisions, Yuma decides to run away from his problems and search for his father until Master Roku confronts him, forcing him to face a few hard truths.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Ruffled Feathers
programme.desc: The race for entry into the World Duel Carnival sees Nistro clash with TV superhero The Sparrow.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Family Leave
programme.desc: Trey makes an unexpected visit to Yuma’s house and discovers the secret behind Yuma’s incredible dueling skills.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Sky's the Limit
programme.desc: After accepting Trey’s challenge to a duel, Yuma soon learns that Trey has acquired a dark and dangerous new power.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Exit: Astral
programme.desc: With the bond between Astral and Yuma broken, Trey takes aim at the rest of Yuma’s life points.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Crestfallen
programme.desc: The back-and-forth battle between Trey and Yuma reaches its climactic conclusion! Can Yuma defeat Trey without Astral’s assistance or will Trey triumph, leaving Yuma one Heart Piece short of making it to the finals?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Party Panic
programme.desc: Yuma and his friends get all decked out for the event of the year - the World Duel Carnival Finals party! But when Yuma forgets his invite, can he find a way into the festivities, or will he be forced to hit the road and head home early?!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Hack Attack
programme.desc: Blue Angel swoops in from the blue to save Playmaker from two AIs designed to destroy!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Blue’s Back!
programme.desc: Blue Angel continues her duel against an AI whose prime directives are: duel, decimate, delete!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Dueling for Answers
programme.desc: Playmaker battles Zaizen to unlock Sol Tech’s databank and the secrets to his past!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: The Lost Incident
programme.desc: The chilling details of the past are finally revealed as Playmaker continues his battle with Zaizen.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: A Piece of the Puzzle
programme.desc: Zaizen has the upper hand, but Playmaker’s looking to make one last play to take him down!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Story Time!
programme.desc: Ai updates Roboppi’s processors on the who, what, where, and why of LINK VRAINS!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: The Deleted
programme.desc: Duelists are mysteriously being logged into LINK VRAINS against their will, and it’s up to Yusaku to find out why!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: A Grim Tale
programme.desc: When a Ph.D. in DNA challenges Gore to a duel, the prognosis is positively grim!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: To Gore Or Not To Gore
programme.desc: Can Gore turn his duel around before the doctor of DNA deletes him!
programme.sub-title: To Gore Or Not To Gore

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 803
programme.desc: Natasja er tidligere side-9-pige og model. I 2013 fik hun skiftet implantaterne i silikonebrysterne ud, men operationen gik ikke som planlagt, og som resultat har hun nu to meget forskellige bryster.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 406
programme.desc: I dette afsnit møder vi Anita, der vågner op med større bryster, end hun forinden havde aftalt med kirurgen og nu føler sig som en miniudgave af Linse Kessler.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 404
programme.desc: Vi møder Maria, der efter en brystforstørrende operation fik store bylder og hul helt ind til implantatet og Casper, der hele livet er blevet mobbet med sin næse, og blev opereret – til næsens kollaps.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 403
programme.desc: Vi møder Charlotte, der har svært ved at få et forhold til en mand, fordi hun skammer sig over sine silikonebryster, og Katja, som kæmper med gamle tråde fra tidligere operationer i brysterne.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 612
programme.desc: Efter et større vægttab får 25-årige Michele lavet en maveskindsoperation, men resultatet skuffer slemt, og Michele har fået store problemer med sin livskvalitet.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 602
programme.desc: Carina har fået fjernet hudkræft på næsen og får i 2012 foretaget en rekonstruktion med egen hud. I dag er hun så ked af sin næse, at hun ikke vil være med på familiebilleder.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 904
programme.desc: Jeanne får uønskede og sårende tilråb for sine nye bryster, og de hæmmer hende fra at leve et normalt liv. Gitte skammer sig over sine ben og bruger enormt meget tid og energi på at kamuflere dem.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 509
programme.desc: Philip fik som 16-årig brækket næsen i en slåskamp og har siden forsøgt at få den pæn gennem en række operationer i udlandet. Alle operationerne er mislykkedes.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 106
programme.desc: I mit plastikmareridt møder vi fire ofre for plastiskkirurgiske fejloperationer. Lone, der lever i frygt for at hendes implantater er kræftfremkaldende.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 705
programme.desc: Fejlslagne plastikoperationer har givet tre patienter ar på både krop og sjæl. Nu står to af landets dygtigste plastikkirurger igen klar til at tilbyde deres hjælp.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 506
programme.desc: I 2010 får Birthe indsat saltvandsimplanater i stedet for de almindelige silikoneimplantater. 5 år senere vågner hun op til et skræmmende syn - hendes ene implantat er væk.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 306
programme.desc: Vi møder bl.a. Jeanette, der føler sig som en forsøgskanin efter en række mislykkede operationer og Shahin, som lever i et smertehelvede efter en ansigtsløftning, hun blev overtalt til på en klinik i Litauen.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 605
programme.desc: Da Annika fylder 30 år, får hun sin penge til en skønhedsoperation af sin mand. Parret rejser sammen til Litauen, men allerede på operationsdagen opdager Annika, at den litauiske kirurg ikke gør, hvad de har aftalt.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 203
programme.desc: Mød Pia, der efter en brystforstørrende operation fik stafylokokker og måtte gå 6 måneder med kun ét implantat hun først fik ud, da hun fik blodforgiftning.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 301
programme.desc: Fejlslagne plastikoperationer har givet fire kvinder ar på både krop og sjæl. Vi møder Jane, som har fået ødelagt sin karriere som dildosælger af, at hun ikke længere selv har lyst til sex på grund af sine grimme bryster.

programme.title: Mit plastikmareridt: Episode 104
programme.desc: I Mit Plastikmareridt møder vi fire ofre for plastiskkirurgiske fejloperationer. Gitte, hvis maveoperation er sunket ned i hendes underliv.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Lola The Bunny
programme.desc: Påskesøndag: På Jersey-maner. Kaninen Lola vender tilbage. Angelina og Snooki hærger en vingård. Bofællerne nyder San Diegos havnefront.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Dren
programme.desc: Dren (navneord): Snookis alter ego. Pauly og Nikki ankommer, og bofællerne møder dyrene. Men løver, tigre og bjørne er det rene vand i forhold til Snooki, da Dren kaprer Nikkis fødselsdag.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The Staten Island Notebook
programme.desc: Dren fortsætter sit angreb på San Diego. Der foregår noget mellem Angelina og Vinny. Og da bofællerne besøger San Diegos Little Italy overraskes de af den ultimative guido - onkel Nino.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Wild "N Out: Jersey Style
programme.desc: Deenas familiedag får Angelina til at mindes sit fejlslagne ægteskab. Jenni ryger på skadestuen. Og Nick Cannon og Justina Valentine fører bofællerne gennem et improviseret spil Wild 'N Out. Må den sjoveste guido vinde!

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Knock Knock! Who's There?
programme.desc: Vand forvandles til vin og på et splitsekund opstår der totalt kaos mellem Pauly, Nikki og Angelina.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Another Day, Anoter Crisis
programme.desc: Angelina sætter sig for at stifte fred med Pauly og Nikki. Vinny planlægger Vin-Dag. Mike og Vinny dyster på et brasiliansk bøfhus. Hvem spiser mest kød?

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Jersey Shore Family Vacation
programme.desc: Vin-Dag-aktiviteterne starter! Flokken starter med sjippen og cykling. Og så shots! Ingefærshots. Efter middagen tager alle på stripklub for at afslutte Vin-Dag.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Reunion Part 1
programme.desc: Tv's bedste italienske familie genforenes og holder sig ikke tilbage... er Angeliners endelig blevet skilt? Og er gamle Sitch en saga blot?

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Reunion Part 2
programme.desc: Jeres yndlingsbofæller er ikke færdige! Vinny og Angelina bliver frække, Kødbollerne omfavner deres vilde side, og stemningen bliver så ophedet at én bofælle er nødt til at køle ned.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Where's the Charcuterie?
programme.desc: Bofællerne støtter Mike, der tager afsked med sin elskede hund Mosey.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Sliding Into DMs
programme.desc: Snooki forvandler Deena, Angelina og JWoww til et heppekor. Mike gestalter Rocky, mens han træner til Super Hole 3 Corn Hole-mesterskaberne.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Lake Jersey
programme.desc: En helt normal dag ved søen med sejlads, druk, skænderier og skøddans.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Life Of A Cornstar
programme.desc: Hvad venter der Angelina, nu da hun har røbet sine sande følelser for Vinny? Og med Pauly D's ord bliver et slag Sandhed eller Konsekvens "Pinlig!".

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Get Your Sack In The Hole
programme.desc: Mike vil vinde det hele. Gnavne Gamling vil i seng. Snooki vil sætte ild til ting.
programme.sub-title: Get Your Sack In The Hole

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Messy Mamas
programme.desc: Vinny inviterer Angelina til sin lejlighed... er det en date? Nicole inviterer pigerne til Californien på forretningsrejse/vild weekend i vindistriktet.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Party in Portugal!
programme.desc: Sam træffer en stor beslutning, da slænget får at vide, at de skal til Portugal. På trods af det, fester familien løs i Algarve. Men spændingerne mellem Bethan, Beau og Abbie truer med at koge over og ødelægge ferien.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Agg on the Algarve!
programme.desc: Bethan og Abbies skænderi påvirker alle i huset, og det begynder, da Nat kalder Bethan og Beaus forhold giftigt. Men i sand Geordie-stil lægger familien det bag sig, tager en sangria og går i byen!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Fun at the Fair!
programme.desc: Slænget vender hjem fra Portugal, men Sam har forladt huset og Chloe tror, det er forbi. Familien besøger Newcastles største marked og Beau spørger endelig Bethan om hun vil være hans kæreste.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Geordies Do the Great Outdoors!
programme.desc: Chloe besøger Sam, og det går fremad med deres forhold mens de andre beslutter at gå i byen klædt som det modsatte køn. Slænget tager på campingtur og James beslutter at fortælle Sam om Chloes kys på Ibiza.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Breaking Point
programme.desc: James fortæller Sam om Chloes kys på Ibiza, og helvede bryder løs, da Sam konfronterer hende. Chloe er chokeret over, at Abbie fortalte hemmeligheden, fordi der kun var tale om et kys. Sådan ser Sam det ikke, så hun forlader huset.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Beau's Birthday!
programme.desc: Chloe & Sam er ude af huset, så slænget fokuserer på at have det sjovt. De holder en junglefest for Beau - den er vild! James & Beau overrasker Nathan ved at invitere en potentiel kæreste, Tommy fra Amsterdam, til Newcastle.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Serious Send Off!
programme.desc: Det er den sidste fulde dag i huset, og slænget forbereder sig på den store dag. Nathan lader Bethan vokse ham bagi, Nat laver mad til familien og Chloe støder til alle de andre på en sidste bytur i Newcastle -den bliver vildt!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Get This Party Started!
programme.desc: Geordierne glæder sig til at komme tilbage i huset, og de fleste er single. De byder velkommen til to nye, Amelia og Ant, som de viser, hvordan de fester. Det er sjovt, indtil Nathan og Beau kommer for tæt på hinanden ifølge Bethan.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Family Friction!
programme.desc: Slænget hygger sig med at lære de nye at kende. Anna sender dem på et anderledes job for at levere en undskyldning, og alt går galt, da Chloe kommer lidt for tæt på den nye fyr Ant.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: It's Fright Night!
programme.desc: Chloes følelser for Ant forsvinder, men han tror, der er en chance, da hun lader ham ligge i sin seng. Slænget bliver skrækslagne, da de tager på aftenvandring i skoven, og Abbie og Chloe snakker for første gang i lang tid.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Hello New Lad!
programme.desc: Den nye fyr Louis gør et stort indtryk fra starten. Chloe falder for ham, og det bliver Ant ikke glad for. Slænget holder en vild fest. Ant føler sig ignoreret af Chloe og Bethan vil have mere opmærksomhed af Beau.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Big Mistake!
programme.desc: Louis skælder Chloe ud, fordi hun sagde undskyld til Ant, men så er hun sammen med Ant. Stor fejltagelse! Beau og Bethan aftaler, at dagen er til venner, og natten er til dem, men Beau bliver fuld og kvajer sig.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: See Ya, Nat!
programme.desc: Nat har ikke haft det godt og beslutter at få fjernes sin tatovering med eksens navn, men efter selvransagelse beslutter hun at forlade huset. Beau og Bethan har problemer og tager sig en svær snak om fremtiden.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Chloe Changes Her Ways!
programme.desc: Bethan rejser for at arbejde med sig selv, men Beau bliver hos familien. Til en fest laver Ant ravage mellem Louis og Chloe, og fyrene kommer op at skændes. Chloe beviser, at hun er en stærk, uafhængig kvinde!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Geordie-licious!
programme.desc: Det er sidste aften, og slænget er værter for eventet Geordie-licious! Der er pres på for at levere en fest, som ingen glemmer. Amelia synger, Nathan har kjole på og fyrene stripper! Louis og Chloe taler åbent og lader til at ville det samme.

programme.title: Yo! MTV Raps Classic: Yo! 3rd Anniversary
programme.desc: Fab 5 Freddy showcases past memorable moments on his 3rd anniversary episode of Yo! MTV Raps

programme.title: Yo! MTV Raps Classic: Cypress Hill

programme.title: Zoey 101: Chases bedstemor
programme.desc: Zoey skal finde en fødselsdagsgave til Chase og får en god ide, da hun finder ud af, hans bedstemor har fødselsdag samme dag. Dustin får armen i klemme i en madautomat, så Lola og Quinn må prøve at hjælpe ham fri.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Michael elsker Lisa
programme.desc: Michael bliver distraheret af sin betagelse af Lisa i sit forsøg på at vinde en talentkonkurrence. Logan udfordrer Chase til et gokartløb.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Radioen
programme.desc: Chase arver en gammel radio, som har tilhørt hans bedstefar, men i stedet for at beholde den, sælger han den til Zoey for fem dollars og en taco-kupon. Zoey finder ud af, at radioen er meget mere værd, end det hun har betalt for den.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Tjenestekæden
programme.desc: Zoeys yndlingsforfatter dukker op ved en lokal begivenhed og Zoey får problemer, da hun er desperat for at skaffe en kørelejlighed.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Zoeys Spareribs
programme.desc: Zoey arver en ladning spareribs efter en onkel, hun aldrig har mødt og beslutter at afholde en grillkonkurrence.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Dryppen' Episode
programme.desc: Dustin flipper ud over en gyserfilm og vil væk fra PCA. Brandalarmen på drengenes sovesal ringer uden nogen grund og de beslutter at finde ud af hvorfor.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Paige på PCA
programme.desc: Da et fysikgeni overvejer at begynde på PCA, gør Quinn oprør ved udsigten til at miste sin status som den klogeste pige på skolen. Michael er bange for, at han er ved at miste forstanden.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Dekanens søn
programme.desc: Zoey begynder at date dekanens søn, og befinder sig hurtigt midt i en lotteriskandale. Chase og Michael producerer online-tegnefilm og bliver sagsøgt for at krænke ophavsretten.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Hænderne på Blix-bilen
programme.desc: Vennerne vil forsøge at vinde en rejse til et valgfrit rejsemål, ved at holde deres hænder på en Blix-sponsoreret bil. Quinn bruger tiden på at opfinde en mundspray, der tilfældigvis forårsager ustandselig latter.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Dansekonkurrencen
programme.desc: Den klodsede Chase går til dansekonkurrence med Zoey, efter at hans tidligere dansepartner brækker benet. Lola narrer en beundrer til at tro, hun er brite.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Miss PCA
programme.desc: Lola og Zoey deltager i en skønhedskonkurrence, men deres rivaliseren ender med et kæmpe opgør. Michael er fast besluttet på at få Quinn til at synes, han er morsom.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Logan bliver afskåret
programme.desc: Rige Logan står over for en forandring i livsstil, da hans enorme forbrug får hans far til at smække kassen i. Michael påstår, han kan slippe fri af enhver bundet knude, så Mark og Quinn binder ham for at se, hvad han vil stille op.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Farvel, Zoey? Del 1
programme.desc: Zoey skal beslutte, om hun vil blive på PCA eller flytte til London med sine forældre. Hun spørger vennerne til råds, men undgår Chase indtil sidste øjeblik. Da hun endelig vil tale med ham, ignorerer han hende, fordi han er fornærmet.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Farvel, Zoey? Del 2
programme.desc: Zoey skal beslutte, om hun vil blive på PCA eller flytte til London med sine forældre. Hun spørger vennerne til råds, men undgår Chase indtil sidste øjeblik. Da hun endelig vil tale med ham, ignorerer han hende, fordi han er fornærmet.

programme.title: Zoey 101: PCA Confidential
programme.desc: Fremtidige elever får et kig bag kulissen til livet på PCA.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Falsk slof
programme.desc: Michael og Logan forsøger at narre Miss Burvitch for at undgå at få tildelt en ny slof. Zoey får utilsigtet Coco fyret, og prøver at hjælpe hende med at få sit job tilbage.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Alene på PCA
programme.desc: Vennerne morer sig på skolen, da deres ferie er blevet aflyst, men spasen slutter da drengene bliver anklaget for hærværk.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Kærlighedsrygter
programme.desc: Michael og Logans nye slof viser sig at være en lækker fyr, der hurtigt opnår popularitet hos pigerne på skolen. Der opstår et rygte om at James og Zoey dater, og de vil finde ud af, hvem der har startet dette rygte.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Vredeskontrol
programme.desc: Logan sende Dustin en hidsig talemeddelelse, som resulterer i en plads på et vredeskontrolkursus. Han prøver at undslippe, ved at være rolig, men Zoey har andre planer.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Quinn savner Mark
programme.desc: Quinn og Mark aftaler at holde pause fra hinanden, men Quinn bliver vred, da hun ser ham med en anden pige. Quinn finder uventet trøst hos Logan, og det fører til, at de kysser hinanden. I mellemtiden følger en hest efter Michael på skolen.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ombytningen
programme.desc: Zoey vender tilbage til PCA for at tale med Chase, men hun finder snart ud af, han er flyttet til England for at være sammen med hende. Da Zoey og Chase taler sammen, afslører Chase, at han skal blive boende i London et helt skoleår.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Gåmaraton
programme.desc: Zoey prøver at hjælpe Lola med at skaffe nogle penge, hun har lovet at donere i forbindelse med et "walk-aton". I mellemtiden kommer Quinn og Logan tættere på hinanden, men prøver at holde det hemmeligt.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Vince er tilbage
programme.desc: Vennerne overraskes, da den tidligere plageånd, Vince Blake, vender tilbage til PCA. Pigerne beslutter at ignorere ham, men det er ikke lige let for alle. Drengene planlægger hævn over Vince.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Kaffevognsforbuddet
programme.desc: Dekanen forbyder kaffevogne på skolen efter et uheld, der involverer hans kone. Der bliver krig mellem drengene og pigerne om at finde den smarteste måde at omgå forbuddet på.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Rutsjebanen
programme.desc: Vennerne tager på klasseudflugt og vil have en tur i en rutsjebane, men det betyder nedtur for Michael, der skal konfrontere sin angst for rutsjebaner.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Jagten på Zoey, første del
programme.desc: Zoey planlægger en tur til Maui i sommerferien og James vil også med, men Zoeys reaktion på dette bliver uventet ubehageligt for ham. Michael får en bil af sin far, så han kan køre Lisa til skoleballet.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Jagten på Zoey, anden del
programme.desc: Zoey planlægger en tur til Maui i sommerferien og James vil også med, men Zoeys reaktion på dette bliver uventet ubehageligt for ham. Michael får en bil af sin far, så han kan køre Lisa til skoleballet.

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Hvad skete der?
programme.desc: Der opstår spændinger mellem de bedste veninder, Louise og Monica, da Louise inviterer den mystiske outsider, Thais, til en hemmelig fest på skolen.

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Den første mistænkte
programme.desc: Efterforskningen bliver kompliceret, da Louise mistænker Monicas kæreste, Peter. Hun kommer i et stort skænderi med Eva efter at have delt en ydmygende video om Eva og Peter til politiet.

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Vælg side
programme.desc: Louise er knust, da hun finder ud af, at Thais måske ikke er så uskyldig, som hun troede. Snart vender Monica og hele skolen sig mod ham og beskylder ham for voldtægten.

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Hemmeligt begær
programme.desc: Efterforskningen tager en ny drejning, da Thais deler kompromitterende oplysninger om Mikkels færden den aften, hvor voldtægten fandt sted. Louise må vælge, hvem hun skal stole på – Mikkel eller Thais?

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Bedrageriske hjerter
programme.desc: Da Louise fortæller Monica, at hun gerne vil være sammen med Thais, afslører Monica, hvad der skete mellem hende og Thais i fortiden. Hvor godt kender Louise egentlig Thais?

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Skru tiden tilbage
programme.desc: Da Thais bliver hentet af politiet, lader det til, at gåden er løst. Alle vil bare gerne starte forfra. Men folk har ændret sig, og uskyldens dage er forbi.

programme.title: Håber du kom godt hjem: Det kan aldrig blive som før

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Sun Spirit Unleashed
programme.desc: The day of the Holy Road semi-final is here! Raimon, confident in their quest to restore "real" football, takes on the "perfect" Universal Middle School. But Arion sees a familiar face on the opposing sideline.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Arion versus Sol
programme.desc: Victor has shocking words for Arion: "You're the only one on Raimon who isn't playing seriously right now." Arion wonders if it's because of his concern for Sol Daystar, whose illness makes him too weak to withstand the rigors of the game.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Arion, the New Captain
programme.desc: The match against Universal is over, and Riccardo, who fell during the game, is undergoing emergency surgery. This puts the team captain out for the upcoming Holy Road championship, a major blow to Raimon's hopes.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Showdown in Zenith Stadium
programme.desc: A battered Victor tells a surprised Arion they must learn a certain special move if they hope to win. As Arion guides Raimon as captain, he secretly engages in a series of gruelling practices right up to the night before the championship.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Double Jeopardy, Part 1
programme.desc: After accidentally falling asleep, Flip wakes up to a nightmare realization – he just slept through the first day of the World Duel Carnival.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Double Jeopardy, Part 2
programme.desc: With Astral missing, Yuma must rely on his skills alone if he wants to defeat Nistro and Dextra and save his deck and spot in the World Duel Carnival.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Pets Peeved
programme.desc: When Yuma's Heart Pieces are swiped by a pack of stray dogs, Cathy calls on her feline friends to help hunt them down. After finding the hounds' hideout, Cathy is challenged by the pack leader to a duel.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: About Hart
programme.desc: After using his powers to escape from Heartland City, Hart unleashes a path of destruction that only Yuma can help stop!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Losing Hart
programme.desc: As Kite desperately searches for his brother, Vetrix puts his diabolical plan for revenge in motion.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: A Dubious Duo
programme.desc: Vetrix continues his quest to drain Hart of all his powers.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: The Dragon Awakens
programme.desc: Kite must learn to work with Yuma if he wants to take down Trey and Quattro and rescue Hart. Can Kite put his pride aside and accept Yuma’s help, or will Kite’s ego end up sacrificing Hart’s safety?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Dragon Link, the Ultimate Foe
programme.desc: The Holy Road championship, the match that decides who becomes the next Holy Emperor, is finally here! An evenly fought first half ends with Fifth Sector's strongest and the freedom fighters of Raimon tied--a development that pleases Raimon to no end.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Final Holy War
programme.desc: The second half begins with all of Mount Olympus' players substituted out. Gyan Cinquedea, creator of Fifth Sector, serves as coach, and Raimon is now faced with his DRAGON LINK team.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Bring our Games to the Heavens
programme.desc: Arion's anti-DRAGON LINK strategy fails, causing more damage to Raimon than the opposing team. Losing confidence and feeling worthless, Arion is ready to surrender when a certain someone suddenly appeals to him.
programme.sub-title: Bring our Games to the Heavens

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Pass to the Future
programme.desc: The battle against DRAGON LINK is over, and the world of football is free once more. Because Raimon's team of skilled players trusted in each other, they restored the ultimate kind of football.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The TV Reporter is here
programme.desc: The fiercely contested Holy Road final is finally over, and the TV cameras have come to Raimon to film a special about Arion and the team who have breathed new life into the game of football.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: This is Raimon Football Club
programme.desc: Continuing on from the previous episode’s look at the current Raimon team, this time we take a look at the history of Raimon’s football club, as told by Coach Evans.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Let’s play soccer!
programme.desc: Mark Evans is the captain of the Raimon Middle School’s long-neglected soccer club. With the club on the verge of being disbanded Mark is hoping to kick it into shape, but he’ll need a little help and more than a little luck.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Royal is here!
programme.desc: Raimon have gotten their first piece of good news, they’re going to play an exhibition game! Except that the game is against the toughest team in the whole country.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the killer shot!
programme.desc: The team are still on a high from their surprise win against Royal Academy, but there’s a lot of work they still need to do. Kevin is mad at himself and jealous of Axel for scoring the winning shot.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the Dragon!
programme.desc: It’s game day for Raimon and they’re playing a team that everyone’s nervous about - Occult Jr High.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Where's the notebook?
programme.desc: The Soccer Frontier Tournament is about to start and Raimon are up against the terrifying jumpers of Wild Junior High in their first game. Everyone agrees that unless they come up with a new move, Raimon are finished before they even start.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is the Inazuma Drop!
programme.desc: Raimon are all pumped up and ready for their big game against Wild Junior High, all except one player - Jack Wallside. His fear of heights is getting in the way of the Inazuma Drop, and without it all is lost.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: On Your Mark, Get Set, DUEL!
programme.desc: Hoping to save his friends from the clutches of Sector Security, Yusei Fudo challenges his old nemesis Officer Trudge to a Turbo Duel!
programme.sub-title: On Your Mark, Get Set, DUEL!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: Creepy Crawlies
programme.desc: With his Duel Runner on the line, Yusei finds himself dueling against a bully who battles with a deck full of bugs.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: Pipe Dreams
programme.desc: Looking to get his Stardust Dragon card back from Jack Atlas, Yusei takes off in a race against time and Sector Security.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: A Blast from the Past, Part 1
programme.desc: After making it through to New Domino City, Yusei confronts his old friend Jack Atlas and challenges him to a Turbo Duel.
programme.sub-title: A Blast from the Past, Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: A Blast from the Past, Part 2
programme.desc: As the clash between Jack and Yusei comes to a climatic close, a mysterious creature appears as their two Dragons duke it out.
programme.sub-title: A Blast from the Past, Part 2

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the Dragon!
programme.desc: It’s game day for Raimon and they’re playing a team that everyone’s nervous about - Occult Jr High.

programme.desc: The Soccer Frontier Tournament is about to start and Raimon are up against the terrifying jumpers of Wild Junior High in their first game. Everyone agrees that unless they come up with a new move, Raimon are finished before they even start.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is the Inazuma Drop!
programme.desc: Raimon are all pumped up and ready for their big game against Wild Junior High, all except one player - Jack Wallside. His fear of heights is getting in the way of the Inazuma Drop, and without it all is lost.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Showdown at the riverbank!
programme.desc: Raimon are training hard for the next game in the Soccer Frontier Tournament, and people are beginning to sit up and take notice; including their next opponents - Brainwashing Jr High.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The terrifying soccer cyborgs!
programme.desc: It’s another big game for Raimon, against the robots of Brainwashing Jr High. Nobody’s ever scored a goal against them, much less won, but if Raimon want to advance they have to do just that.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Willy rising!
programme.desc: Axel Blaze is injured and out of Raimon’s next game, but their opponents are the weakest team in the whole tournament, so winning shouldn’t be a problem.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The spy from Royal
programme.desc: Raimon Jr Soccer Club is looking stronger than ever, but so are the forces in league against them.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Find a new coach
programme.desc: The big game against Royal is only a few days away, but unless Raimon Jr can find a new coach then they’re going out without even setting foot on the field!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The finals - Royal Academy - first half!
programme.desc: The boys arrive at Royal Academy for the biggest game of their lives, but before they can begin they have to dispel the cloud of suspicion hanging over the place.
programme.sub-title: The finals - Royal Academy - first half!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The finals - Royal Academy - second half!
programme.desc: With Ray Dark safely shut away, the game against Royal has properly begin, and it’s a real game this time not a walkover. It’s neck and neck and back and forth and the air is full of penguins.
programme.sub-title: The finals - Royal Academy - second half!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Legendary 11!
programme.desc: The boys still can't believe they beat Royal and are the new District Champion. After the celebratory dust settles, a mysterious figure walks into Seymour’s noodle bar.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is it - the National tournament!
programme.desc: The Raimon 11 have set their sights on the National tournament and they’re determined to win it all.
programme.sub-title: This is it - the National tournament!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Soccer - ninja style!
programme.desc: With Nathan still on the team, for now, the Raimon 11 can move forward and concentrate on the Nationals.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Jude's decision!
programme.desc: The narrow victory over Shuriken has given Raimon confidence, but on the other side of the tournament there’s shock and awe at Royal’s complete destruction at the hands of Zeus Jr.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Break the unbreakable wall!
programme.desc: With their firepower boosted by the addition of Jude Sharp, the team are ready to tackle Farm Jr High and their unbreakable defence. But unless they get their passes coordinated then all their hard work will come to nothing!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The reincarnated genius!
programme.desc: Erik the Eagle is back! Like a phoenix he has risen from the ashes and come back to visit his old friend. Just in time too, Raimon Jr are desperate for some new moves, and the Tri Pegasus is just what they need. But can they perfect it in time?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The killer Triangle Z!
programme.desc: Raimon Jr are getting ready to play their next big opponent - Kirkwood Jr High, which just happens to be Axel Blaze’s old school.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The clash with Kirkwood Jr. High!
programme.desc: The Murdock brothers and their grudge are dominating Raimon Jr. at every turn, but they need to find the strength to overcome their malice if they’re going to make it to the final. If they don’t work together, their dream is finished!
programme.sub-title: The clash with Kirkwood Jr. High!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Go beyond the God Hand!
programme.desc: Raimon Jr. are through to the finals, but they’re all getting nervous about playing the terrifying Zeus Jr. Mark is convinced he’s not good enough, and if that weren’t enough to rattle nerves

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: A challenge from a God!
programme.desc: As the final against Zeus draws nearer, so does Raimon Jr’s anticipation and dread. The team are working hard, but the level they have to reach seems beyond their grasp. Will they get it together in time for the final?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Time for training camp!
programme.desc: The big game is almost on top of them but Mark still hasn’t mastered Majin the Hand. The coach decides to try and new tactic and everyone spends the night at school at a sleepover training camp.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The final battle!
programme.desc: This is it, the final of the Nationals has arrived. Zeus Jr. storm to an early lead and nothing Raimon Jr does has any effect on them. Are they really gods? Or is something else going on?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: God vs Majin!
programme.desc: Raimon Jr. are down by three goals and are getting clobbered by the soccer gods of Zeus Jr. The situation looks completely hopeless and the clock is running down.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Aliens Are Here!
programme.desc: The victory for the Raimon 11 proves to be very short lived, as only a few minutes after their win, the sky falls in. Literally! - All of a sudden the earth is overrun by aliens!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Raimon 11 Fight Back!
programme.desc: The Raimon 11 have stepped up to try and save the world against the soccer players of Alius Academy, but it’s like pitting an ant against an elephant.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Take Down the Black 11!
programme.desc: The president has been kidnapped by aliens, and Mark and the others are determined to help him. The Inazuma Caravan travels to the park where he was kidnapped, ready to beat the aliens off.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Alius Academy Threat
programme.desc: The tenacious Raimon 11 players never give up, and they’re going to try again against Alius Academy. But try as they might they can't even hold a candle to them.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Search for the Legendary Striker!
programme.desc: The news that Axel is kicked off the team doesn’t go over well with most of the Raimon players, especially Kevin Dragonfly.
programme.sub-title: The Search for the Legendary Striker!

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: The Bunker, Pt. 2
programme.desc: While trying to free a nuclear scientist and his wife from enemy hands, the IMF is trapped when a would-be assassin takes over one of Rollin's disguises in Part 2.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: Nitro
programme.desc: The IMF finds itself only a second away from eternity when they intercept a nitroglycerine expert who plans to blow up the government house of a small country, thus provoking war with its neighbor nation.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: The Vault
programme.desc: Guest star Nehemiah Persoff as a corrupt Latin American official plots to loot his own country of $40,000,000 with the connivance of the IMF.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: Nicole
programme.desc: Guest star Joan Collins, as a seductive double agent, endangers a vital IMF project when Jim Phelps falls in love with her.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: Illusion
programme.desc: Cinnamon and Rollin become cabaret performers in a plot to get a deranged man (guest Fritz Weaver) to fall in love with Cinnamon, then kill her.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: The Interrogator
programme.desc: In a bold experiment with a man's mind, the IMF blanks out an enemy agent's memory (guest star Henry Silva), then sets out to make him think he is someone else.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: The Controllers (Part 1)
programme.desc: Leonard Nimoy and guest star Dina Merrill join the Impossible Missions Force to fight a mind-destroying drug that could enslave the free world in the first of a two-part episode.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: The Controllers (Part 2)
programme.desc: Jim Phelps lets himself be framed for murder in a scheme to discredit a scientist who has developed a mind-destroying drug in the second of a two-part episode on Paramount Television's "Mission: Impossible."

programme.title: Mission: Impossible: The Code

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 4
programme.desc: Advanced Nurse Practitioner Cheryl Barnes answers the red phone and heads to resus. ‘When that red phone rings it gives you a bit of an adrenaline rush, but I don’t think that’s a bad thing.’

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 5
programme.desc: Battling to keep the flow of patients moving is Sister Jane Hawksworth but she’s got a problem. They’re two porters down and it’s causing a backlog, but the emergencies keep arriving.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 6
programme.desc: We spend an eventful night shift with Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty team. Evenings are a peak time for road traffic collisions and the most critical cases are blue lit straight to Casualty.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 7
programme.desc: Registrar Doctor Ashleigh Trimble takes the next call from paramedics. 81-year-old Roy is being blue lighted in, after falling over and landing badly on one of his artificial hips.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 8
programme.desc: With an already busy department, Nurse Chloe Wesley answers the red emergency phone. A 23-month-old toddler is being rushed in with suspected sepsis, a life-threatening condition that attacks the internal organs.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 9
programme.desc: Registrar Doctor Rob Cornford heads straight to Resus to treat 58-year-old window-fitter Craig who’s been blue-lighted in. He was working on a ladder on the first floor of a house when he fell and was knocked unconscious.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 10
programme.desc: Sister Jane Hawksworth has clocked on for a night shift to find every bed in Barnsley Hospital is taken. To get the department moving again Sister Jane and the close-knit Casualty team will have to pull together.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 11
programme.desc: Sister Benita Wainwright is leading the team, a day that she describes as “Chaos. There are people everywhere. It’s hard going. But staff pull together and make sure patients are looked after.”

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 12
programme.desc: At Barnsley Casualty the team clock on to a backlog of patients waiting to be transferred to wards. With no beds across the entire hospital, Sister Jane Hawksworth is battling to prevent patients being on trolleys for the NHS maximum of 12 hours.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 13
programme.desc: After an extraordinarily busy few days, the team at Barnsley Casualty are struggling to clear the backlog of patients, and new arrivals are waiting up to 5 hours to see a doctor.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 14
programme.desc: Sister Jane Hawksworth is on duty, ‘I think the sister team is strong, we are all strong women.' Sister Benita Wainwright heads to Resus where paramedics rush in a 14-year-old girl having a prolonged epileptic seizure.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 15
programme.desc: It’s been a busy night at Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty Department, so the corridors are already packed full of patients when Sister Benita Wainwright arrives to head the shift.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 16
programme.desc: In charge today at Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty Department is Consultant Doctor Julian Humphrey, ‘Emergency departments may look very chaotic but there’s a reasonable amount of structure. It’s organized chaos!’

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 17
programme.desc: Barnsley Casualty is facing one of its toughest shifts to date. With no children’s beds available across the whole of Yorkshire and a department filling up with poorly children the hospital is under pressure.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 18
programme.desc: Registrar Doctor Gemma Hartshorne prepares to treat a man who has suddenly lost all feeling in his foot. Loss of blood flow is turning Roger's foot white - urgent treatment is needed to prevent amputation.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 1
programme.desc: In this episode we meet 63-year-old Jane, a retired nurse from Southeast London. Jane’s inability to start a family brought on her hoarding tendencies and 27 years later, her 2 bedroomed terrace home is full to the rafters with furniture and books.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 2
programme.desc: From the outside 69-year-old Barbara’s house in Braintree looks like any other on the street, but she wasn’t always a hoarder, as the tragic deaths of her husband and son sent her life spiraling out of control.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 3
programme.desc: In West London, former exotic dancer Dione’s flat is bursting at the seams with a lifetimes collection of memorabilia and hand me down relics. Help is at hand as deep cleaning arrive to clear the hoard.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 4
programme.desc: In the South Wales Valleys, 42-year-old Phillip has it all, he runs a successful business, he’s in a long-term relationship, he owns his own home and... he has a rat infested, humongous hoard.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 10
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Linda and husband Andy from Bedau in South Wales whose house is overrun with animals and hasn’t been cleaned in 4 years.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 11
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Joanna from Birmingham, whose 2-bedroom flat is overflowing with possessions. Joanna works two jobs, leaving her no time to look after her home.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 12
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Alan, a sound therapist who has lived on his own for 20 years. His son has tried to help him clean, but it’s a battle he’s never been able to win.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 1
programme.desc: Hoarding is on the rise and it's believed that 1 in 20 people could have a problem. With over 1.2 million problem hoarders in the UK today, one could be your neighbour?

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 2
programme.desc: Susan's hoard has made her virtually homeless. Brian has dedicated his life to hoarding and his daughter is sick of it. Jake is lucky to be alive as his home almost burned to the ground in an inferno fuelled by the clutter he'd collected.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 3
programme.desc: Arthur's flat is packed with junk. Experts Caz and Tee are up for their toughest assignment ever. Khim is getting married but first she must clear her hoard. Mandi's passion for vintage clothes is out of control.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 4
programme.desc: Esther's hoard is so bad her landlord told her to clear up or clear out. Nigel receives a visit from fellow hoarder Janice.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 1
programme.desc: In this brand-new series of Dirty Home Rescue, Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Toni from Telford whose house is so dirty her partner of 10 years, Rich, won’t move in with her.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 2
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Bill and Antionette from Newport, who share their home with their 3 cats. They admit they’ve not deep cleaned their home since they moved in.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 3
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of married couple Lynne and Keith from Chudleigh in South Devon whose house hasn’t had a deep clean since they moved in nearly 20 years ago.

programme.title: Ekstreme samlere: Episode 5
programme.desc: Paul's hoard fills his whole house, room after room after room is buried under 6 feet of clutter.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Cricket and Hemingway & Rigby
programme.desc: Musicians Ashlee Simpson-Wentz and "Fall Out Boy" Pete Wentz, are concerned at the aggression coming from Hemingway, their English bulldog, especially since they are expecting their first child.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Bacchus and Jody
programme.desc: Jody, a Lhasa apso, cannot keep her mouth off of anything. From tissues to money, she is the dog who ate your homework and then some. She will eat just about everything in sight.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Stanley, Shoven and Leo
programme.desc: Stanley, a surly Chihuahua mix, has a problem with attacking joggers. Two Pomeranians are known for their shrill barks. Shelter rescue Leo, performs a tight rope act when hearing a cough.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Hyde & Vada and Nacho
programme.desc: Hyde and Vada, both wolf hybrids have aggression issues to work out especially when it comes to other dogs. Nacho, bit a child, and shows aggression when he has his toy.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Sadie and Calder
programme.desc: Allen and Erin Carrasco ‘s Basset Hound Sadie whines and moans whenever Allen is around. Blue Heeler mix Calder is a great dog by day, but bedtime rituals unleash unwelcome night terrors.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Chihuahuas from Hell
programme.desc: This one-hour special highlights the demonic demeanors of one of the most challenging breeds, Chihuahuas. Cesar revisits the stories of past participants, Paris, Bandit, and NuNu amongst others.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Charlotte, Elvis and Jack
programme.desc: Actress Eileen Davidson's Wheaten terrier puppy Charlotte, plays too rough with her son. Two other dogs react to household triggers, the garbage disposal and shiny floors.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Cesar and the Horse Whisperer (Chloe & Hobo, Ali)
programme.desc: Cesar enlists the help of Horse Whisperer Pat Parelli at a riding center that works with special needs people. A dog with separation anxiety exhibits extreme dog aggression.
programme.sub-title: Cesar and the Horse Whisperer (Chloe & Hobo, Ali)

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Inside Puppy Mills
programme.desc: This powerful episode delves into the horror of puppy mills and the rescue and rehab of traumatized pups by the Last Chance for Animals non-profit organization.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Nuna & Kane
programme.desc: NuNu the Chihuahua, fiercely attacks anyone who comes near his owner Tina. NuNu’s total opposite, Kane the Great Dane, is vehemently afraid of shiny surfaces

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Opie & Flirt
programme.desc: Black lab mix Opie is a charmer around people, but frighteningly aggressive around other dogs. Energetic to the point of being neurotic, Chinese Crested Flirt cannot sit still for one moment.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Rana & Ruby
programme.desc: Scared of everything, Ruby the Vischla deals with her neuroses by biting. At the same time, Rana barks every time bread pops in the toaster, or when the microwave goes off, or when the phone rings.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Josh & Boomer
programme.desc: Josh, a Maltese, will not let anyone with a brush or pair of scissors near him without putting up a fight. Boomer, a Chesapeake Bay Retriever, barks incessantly and refuses to come out of the pool.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Harry & Brooks
programme.desc: Harry wants to charge after anything with wheels, including passing cyclists, rollerbladers or skateboarders. Brooks, an Entlebucher, is constantly chasing after light, he is never calm.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Coach & Sueki
programme.desc: Coach, an out of control Boxer, bit a neighbor, seemingly sealing his fate. Coach gets a stay of execution when Cesar Millan comes to the rescue. Sueki refuses to walk on the leash.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Slick & Pepper
programme.desc: Slick, a rare white Puli, is full of phobias. When clients come to Christopher’s photography studio, they are greeted by Pepper’s annoying barking and heel nipping.

programme.title: Hundehviskeren: Ava & Gus
programme.desc: Ava, a Pug/Pekingese swiftly twirls for all occasions, possibly a neurological condition Cesar cannot treat. Gus the Bouvier greets people by throwing his 100 pound body at them.

programme.title: South Park: Heksesønner
programme.desc: Til den årlige halloween-fest kaster en heks en besværgelse, der terroriserer alle i South Park.

programme.title: South Park: Trapper Keeper
programme.desc: Cartman har fået en ny Trapper Keeper. Da han har pralet af den, fortæller en fremmed ham, at den snart vil overtage verden, hvis de ikke destruerer den nu.

programme.title: South Park: Korns seje piratspøgelsemysterium
programme.desc: Drengene plages af dem fra 5.klasse, og South Park bliver løbet over ende af piratspøgelser i denne uhyggelige Halloween-episode.

programme.title: South Park: Infårtion
programme.desc: Mens han er til en gruppeterapitime mod hamstring, bliver Stan fanget i en drøm om skolerådgiveren mr. Mackey.

programme.title: South Park: Wall-Mart er på vej
programme.desc: Da Wall-Mart forvandler South Park til en spøgelsesby, prøver Stan og Kyle at ødelægge forretningen, men en besat Cartman står dem i vejen.

programme.title: South Park: Verdenskrig Zimmerman
programme.desc: Cartman anser Token for at være en trussel mod hele menneskeheden.

programme.title: South Park: Døde kendisser
programme.desc: Michael Jacksons spøgelse nægter at acceptere sin hedengang og efterlader resten af de nylig afdøde berømtheder frustrerede i Skærsilden.

programme.title: South Park: Succubus
programme.desc: Cartman er hos optikeren, en mand der gør nar af hans vægtproblem ved at kalde ham 'Piggy'.

programme.title: South Park: Splattet tomat
programme.desc: Børnene i South Park påstår, at de har set mr. Garrison luske omkring. Indbyggerne er vrede over, at præsidenten skræmmer deres børn.

programme.title: South Park: Regnskov dropskov
programme.desc: Drengene bliver sendt til regnskoven i Costa Rica som led i en turné med koret Getting Gay With Kids.

programme.title: South Park: De levende hjemløses nat
programme.desc: Da en sværm af hjemløse kommer til South Park, udtænker drengene en smart plan for at flytte dem til en anden by, mens forældrene går i panik.

programme.title: South Park: Den ustuearrest-bare
programme.desc: Led og ked af hvordan han bliver behandlet af sine forældre, tager den altid uskyldige Butters den nye vampyr-galskab til sig, lidt for entusiastisk.

programme.title: South Park: Helvede på jord 2006
programme.desc: Det er halloween og Satan arrangerer verdens største kostymebal.

programme.title: South Park: Coon vs. Coon og venner
programme.desc: 'The Coon' viser sig at være endnu ondere end den mørke mester Cthulhu, når han kræver hævn over sine tidligere partnere.

programme.title: South Park: Tegridy Farms
programme.desc: Butters sælger e-cigaretter og alt muligt tilbehør med frugtsmag på skolen. Randy beslutter at flytte familien på landet og begynder at dyrke jorden.

programme.title: South Park: Den uhyggelige fisk
programme.desc: Sharon Marshs tante Flo har gaver med til Shelly og Stan. Shelly får et fantastisk stereoanlæg, men Stans gave er en fisk; der er bare det ved det, at der er noget uhyggeligt over den fisk.

programme.title: South Park: Mareridt på FaceTime
programme.desc: Randys planer for Halloween betyder, at Stan ikke kan lave slik og ballade med sine venner.

programme.title: South Park: Det fattige barn
programme.desc: Kennys forældre bliver anholdt og han kommer i pleje - så nu er Cartman det fattigste barn på skolen! Og en mystisk, maskeret figur fra fortiden vender tilbage.

programme.title: South Park: Pandemi 2: Chokket
programme.desc: Kæmpemarsvin angriber byer rundt om på jorden. Drengene har nøglen til at redde menneskeheden, men de sidder fast i Andesbjergene

programme.title: South Park: Døden
programme.desc: Stans gamle bedstefar forsøger at narre drengene til at slå ham ihjel. I mellemtiden forsøger South Parks forældre at overtale et tv-netværk til at befri luftrummet for Terrance og Philip.

programme.title: South Park: Mr. Hankey, julebæen
programme.desc: Borgmesteren beslutter at indføre et neutralt helligdagstema, som ikke kan fornærme nogen. Kyle mener, at han har svaret.

programme.title: South Park: Mecha Streisand
programme.desc: Cartman og Kyle bliver uvenner over en magisk trekant, som dukker op på en arkæologisk udgravning. Trekanten giver magt til at forandre Barbra Streisand til et forfærdeligt monster.

programme.title: South Park: Jewpacabra
